  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 4 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  delayBetweenCharacters: 0.1
  delayBetweenLines: 2
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - We have once again been able to identify additional complications that may appear
    from the ongoing virus outbreak.
  - Any infected individuals may be seen to have speech that is seemingly irregular
    or inconsistent in coherence without apparent reason.
  - Citizens who experience any symptoms indicative of an infected person should
    contact us via their computer messaging application immediately.
  - AN ADDITIONAL UPDATE
  - The evacuation of citizens is nearing completion.
  - By the evening of tomorrow, all citizens are expected to have been evacuated
    and greater measures will be put into action to remove the virus and reallow
    citizens to inhabit the dome safely.
  - Thank you to all citizens for their compliance and support.
